title: "Google Reaches Play Store Settlement. There's Something Bigger at Stake for Alphabet and Apple."
text: "Google-parent Alphabet has agreed to a $700 million settlement to resolve one of the antitrust claims around its app store. It's a small hit for the technology giant but the bigger battle remains over the billions Alphabet and Apple earn from their dominance of the app economy."

title: "Nvidia Stock Could Face a Tougher 2024 After These 2 Recent Developments"
text: "Intel recently announced plans to launch two new AI chips. Alphabet also unveiled its most powerful tensor processing unit (TPU) AI chips to date."

title: "2 Top Artificial Intelligence Stocks That Could Make You Richer in 2024"
text: "The artificial intelligence boom will continue in 2024. But fundamentals will be increasingly important."
